{"tid":1507971,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"House of Card","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:18:00.000Z","uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a3b01d824d2bdb5d931a903af5d357fa8f2cff","tid":1507971,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:13:36.000Z","msg":"心情沉重,翻睇house of card 暫時逃避現實。重温之後覺得現階段對西方文宣做左好多,下一步係要多d同外國政治人物接觸,遊說佢地更大力度支持香港有更大自治權,對支那採取更強硬態度。但係無大台無領袖下點樣可以同佢地做deal ?政治就係利益輸送分配交易,好似支那跪低同侵侵簽約,我地就會無利用價値。唔應該消極祈求其他人會可憐我地有咩實際行動,相反offer利益make deal先令香港人可以係世界政治賭埸上有一席可以下注<br />\n講咁多係想外交上主動出撃,1C2S下香港無外交係弱點,有雙普選都好,原則上無外交權,等同我地企官方上係支那果邊,200萬人上街外國除左出囗術都做唔到d咩。"},{"pid":"933860a5035820d42e14f8ba21a5ff50f061ba07","tid":1507971,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=39329f77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=5032cadb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=a732271e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"f6a70e941ff406e3dce7e48945e000c1b47058b6","tid":1507971,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"香港人要主